Chicken Run;;65;;97;;G;;This engaging stop-motion, claymation adventure tells the story of an American rooster who falls in love with a gorgeous hen on a British farm. The couple decides to run away from the farm, but they must first contend with the evil farmer who is intent on keeping them under her control. The chickens decide to attempt an escape so they don't get turned into chicken pot pies.;;Animation,Comedy,Kids & family,Adventure;;Peter Lord,Nick Park;;2000;;Mel Gibson,Julia Sawalha,Miranda Richardson,Jane Horrocks,Lynn Ferguson,Imelda Staunton,Benjamin Whitrow,Tony Haygarth,Timothy Spall,Phil Daniels;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chicken_run